data.text:
❝So you've finally come... Riumatsu girls.❞

» Riu is the name, and to fangirl over gay stuff is the game.

— Spanish geek who loves military uniforms, Japanese culture, South Korean singers and memes.

— Intermediate level student of both Japanese and Korean language who keeps trying to improve her skills.

— I enjoy cosplaying and collecting figures, straps and some kpop albums.

— I've been playing video games since I was 6 years old.

— KPOP and KHH enthusiast. Favorite groups are A.C.E, MONSTA X, MAMAMOO and DREAMCATCHER and favorite artists are Huang Zi Tao, Chungha, #GUN, Nafla, Loopy and Simon Dominic. I'm pretty much multifandom.

— When I was little, I used to watch shows like Detective Conan, Mermaid Melody Pichi Pichi Pitch, Futari wa Precure, Konjiki no Gash Bell!! and Shin-Chan but never got too interested and obsessed on it until many years later.

— How I rate the shows: it depends on whether I had fun watching it or not, the art style and the OSTs.

— If I have a nice time watching a show, I will put a high rate. The lower the rating, the less I enjoyed it.

Favourite anime/manga genres: psychological, thriller, police, yokai, shounen, shounen-ai, sports and BL.

Disliked anime/manga genres: mecha, ecchi, harem, isekai. I also hate shota, loli, moe and tsundere charas, and despise shotacon, lolicon and incest.

Favourite games: Pokémon, Kingdom Hearts, Ace Attorney, Harvest Moon, Undertale, Danganronpa, Genshin Impact, Hypnosis Mic, Ensemble Stars, visual novels, otomes, rpg's, BL's.

Nice obsessions that are killing me right now: Genshin Impact and Ensemble Stars hell, Hypnosis Mic songs, ZhongChi/TartaLi feels.
